response.original_title: Log Kya Kahenge? (What will People Say?)
response.overview: RJ Gulnaz defies norms, voicing unity, peace, and resistance.
response.tagline: A 24-year-old RJ from an orthodox Ahmedabad family dares to defy societal expectations, using her radio show to spread unity and peace—while battling the very voices trying to silence her.
response.title: Log Kya Kahenge? (What will People Say?)
